%% Diagram: Rsc Flight Stream Sequence
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant B as Browser
    participant E as Edge / Node\n(SSR + RSC runtime)
    participant DB as Database

    B->>E: GET /products
    E->>E: Render server tree\n(server components)
    E->>DB: Query products
    DB-->>E: Rows
    E-->>B: HTML shell\n+ first Flight chunks
    Note over E,B: Server keeps streaming\nas Suspense boundaries resolve
    E->>DB: Query reviews\n(suspended boundary)
    DB-->>E: Rows
    E-->>B: Flight chunk\nfor reviews subtree
    B->>B: Patch DOM placeholder\n(react-server-dom-* runtime)
    B->>B: Hydrate client islands\n(use client modules)
    Note over B: Server component code\nnever crosses the wire
